</script>
<BR><BR>


Moles are also used as clan animals in some Native American cultures. Tribes with Mole Clans 
include the Creek tribe (whose Mole Clan was named Takusalgi or Tvkusvlke) and the 
Pueblo tribes of New Mexico.

